					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p187087">Re: bsnes-plus and xkas-plus (new debugger and assembler)</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=187087&amp;sid=e820e51bd9482a0409e3ba838f70e595#p187087"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Thu Jan 19, 2017 12:16 am&nbsp;</div></td>
